<item>
            <title>[LU-10480] llapi_printf() prefixes command name to the output</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10480</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;commit 7a16f18ae1ef5d21812c916470022280617c4e91 makes info_callback_default() to prefix program name to the output, and liblustreapi uses a lot to call llapi_info_callback()-&amp;gt;info_callback_default() to output.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;# lfs getstripe /mnt/lustre/file
lfs getstripe: /mnt/lustre/file
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:   lcm_layout_gen:    3
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:   lcm_mirror_count:  1
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:   lcm_entry_count:   3
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:     lcme_id:             1
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:     lcme_flags:          init
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:     lcme_extent.e_start: 0
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:     lcme_extent.e_end:   1048576
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:       lmm_stripe_count:  1
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:       lmm_stripe_size:   1048576
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:       lmm_pattern:       raid0
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:       lmm_layout_gen:    0
lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe: lfs getstripe:       lmm_stripe_offset: 1
lfs getstripe:       lmm_objects:
lfs getstripe:       - 0: { l_ost_idx: 1, l_fid: [0x100010000:0xa:0x0] }
lfs getstripe: 
...
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
